%% Diagram: useEffect synchronization lifecycle on dependency change
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant R as React
    participant E as useEffect
    participant X as External system (chat server)

    U->>R: Mount ChatRoom roomId="alpha"
    R->>E: Run setup with roomId="alpha"
    E->>X: connect("alpha")
    X-->>E: connected

    U->>R: Re-render with roomId="beta"
    R->>E: Run cleanup for "alpha"
    E->>X: disconnect("alpha")
    R->>E: Run setup with roomId="beta"
    E->>X: connect("beta")

    U->>R: Unmount ChatRoom
    R->>E: Run cleanup for "beta"
    E->>X: disconnect("beta")

    Note over R,E: In Strict Mode dev builds, React<br/>also runs setup → cleanup → setup once<br/>at mount to surface missing cleanup.
